{
  "texts": [
    "The training is running on 16×NVIDIA A800 for approximately 19 hours.",
    "We first present the accuracy of our classifier to show its effectiveness in measuring the chart distribution.",
    "Then, we compare our model with previous works in traditional benchmarks and our benchmark.",
    "Also, we provide a group of ablation studies to show the effectiveness of our data engine.",
    "Chart Attributes ClassificationWe compare the performance of classifiers with different backbones (i.e., ResNet50 [25], ConvNeXt [50], and CLIP-Vit [61]) and trainable modules (linear probe [61] and two-layer MLP with focal loss [41])."
  ]
}